{"word":"G113 - ἄθεσμος - áthesmos - ath'-es-mos - Wicked","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄθεσμος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">áthesmos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ath'-es-mos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Wicked</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அக்கிரமக்கார - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"lawless wicked, of one who breaks through the restraints of law and gratifies his lusts"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5087 - τίθημι - títhēmi - tith'-ay-mee/5087\">G5087</a> (in the sense of <i>enacting</i>); <i>lawless</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>criminal:</i> - wicked.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}